{"tid":1244760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[G20前推爆佢] 白宮聯署畀Trump多一個籌碼：Please Liberate Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T12:29:23.000Z","uid":40142,"like":117,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f2b6d68f42eeacda723c06d10b2c99943ef9cd","tid":1244760,"uid":40142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"林鄭沒有自由意志，樣樣野要睇習近平頭，大家都知。<br />\n<br />\n兩次加埋三百萬人上街，林鄭都不走不撤，因為三百萬人上街示威，對佢嚟講冇乜大壓力。佢嘅壓力，只會嚟自一個人，習近平。<br />\n<br />\n面對中美貿易戰，習近平也不是沒有壓力。習近平的壓力，嚟自特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n要對付林鄭，我地要借習近平嘅手。要習近平出手，我地要借特朗普的手。這是很簡單易明的道理。<br />\n<br />\n如何借特朗普的手做事？更加簡單。佢開到口要知道香港人的聲音，&ldquo;I&rsquo;m going to let the protesters speak for themselves&ldquo; （我要給機會令示威者自己講出來）。除咗上街之外，以下嘅白宮聯署，係其中一條絕對有效嘅渠道。<br />\n<br />\n最好就喺6月28號前，即係大阪G20高峰會前簽夠數。記住簽完名之後要email confirm先正式完成。<br />\n<br />\n簽完要傳開去，叫多啲人簽，救救香港，向林鄭呢個人渣全方位反擊！<br />\n<br />\n簽完記得MAIL CONFIRM!! 雖知道人家唔係亂咁CLICK過掣就當係, 謝謝!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7966050e\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation</a>"},{"pid":"96792b2cde683fbe451e74e5d98fc656353e42ff","tid":1244760,"uid":40142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c5567a98e67c9096aef730afe46eee35162786e","tid":1244760,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"037775f2f6153827c49f2ea8e106014d206cb946","tid":1244760,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac2367173987a868686b1731