,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1872ab5979d75b331706acdbc39509bb18690f05","tid":1244760,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173210bc003bad77433fd6c202563e8b672de4c2","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"3萬5 ！繼續！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5275cba4ad166547b89b34623c674d322f5e7c9e","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0vCF7iizpYHjSRVQ6M-reeoUQrjpWBHRgDUFUEN_4C1fquimJhsss-eTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0vCF7iizpYHjSRVQ6M-reeoUQrjpWBHRgDUFUEN_4C1fquimJhsss-eTE&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=676f30b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0vCF7iizpYHjSRVQ6M-reeoUQrjpWBHRgDUFUEN_4C1fquimJhsss-eTE</a><br />\n未簽的快簽～～<br />\n<br />\n文章轉載   作者：楊衛隆<br />\n<br />\n集氣七一，血債票償<br />\n昨日飲早茶時和朋友傾談，被問及香港形勢。我簡單地說，香港犯民主張集氣七一，血債票償。集氣七一的意思是，G20之前香港平靜，沒有示威。當勞侵在六月底G20峰會可以不談香港示威。因為一開口，習大大會話，香港示威早就和平結束，林賤道歉，香港人滿意。<br />\n血債票償就更加嚴重，香港人的血債可以用選票補償，那就沒有美國人的事情。爭取選票的人只是想進入立法會做議員，支持不可能出現自治的港共政權，不想自治。<br />\n當勞侵講到明G20峰會提出香港示威。這個重要時刻平靜下來，叫當勞侵如何為香港人開腔說話，如何牽頭爭取國際社會支持香港自治。沒有國際社會支持，美國對中共和港共官員的制裁不會生效。中共和港共官員的資產分佈世界各地，不是美國單獨制裁就可以湊效。<br />\n習大大在G20峰會前急如鍋上螞蟻，走到俄羅斯，伊朗和北韓找人救命。港共假意道歉又停止送中立法，616示威沒有鎮壓，企圖平息民憤。G20是中共和港共政權的大限。犯民的「集氣七一，血債票償」是最緊急關頭放生港共，意思是叫所有人在G20之前甚麼都不要做，讓習大大可以逃過全球制裁厄運。血債票償是支持港共政權。當然這樣做，因為要加入港共政權享受榮華富貴就不能讓港共政權倒下，當然是先要保住港共，即是集氣七一，才能爭取選票，即是血債票償。這樣做是賣港求榮，不是單純出賣港人，也出賣了支持香港自治的美國茶黨。<br />\n錯過了各國元首聚首一堂的G20，當勞侵要尋求各國支持香港自治，難比登天。再說，當勞侵能夠坐在總統寶座多久，很難說。下任總統對支持香港自治的意向如何，無人知道。錯失了這個機會，不會有下次。"},{"pid":"8f03c5d8e01e866a164ab83525e23c19ada45a57","tid":1244760,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8989bf95d904b64338779f11e4d9669d91b9ce","tid":1244760,"uid":264813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f88be91715fbd51a282c6f004fab03c04c52c5","tid":1244760,"uid":155222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d2b250f13710da87a9b78ad44f37958f65e5264","tid":1244760,"uid":40142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:57:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"48b514e74bc5f7b961c27b529e5288a4f864c093","tid":1244760,"uid":613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:59:24.000Z","msg":"推到夠10萬"},{"pid":"a8967354c26434094168920dcb63a43eb42c77ca","tid":1244760,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:08:16.000Z","msg":"Signed"},{"pid":"11f1379a1972eff61db821f5ad9c6f91a8d047af","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:39:10.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"7233866b6ea8257ee39ab27abf5bc71fbde9e88c","tid":1244760,"uid":130488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:28:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b8cd793397207cc5a1356c7d71b6fd4bfcfeb59","tid":1244760,"uid":8173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a37c801c2c55362c0230e4d094835866f3e7323","tid":1244760,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:37:36.000Z","msg":"介唔介意我開多個post兩邊一齊推？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755a7a5ecf3ebc56468e2ac3d607231ba2772761","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:15.000Z","msg":"就黎四萬"},{"pid":"ed73cd8d34c64239b9e199dc9c4e8670b03c9675","tid":1244760,"uid":82879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7020479d3e34ed24d768bdb33e89ee15c2c724a","tid":1244760,"uid":24180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3880a61da3acd79bdc9593fe64f032c0b1eb75e","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"2f66ff20f790c738782577d03d9966d8bc64c9ea","tid":1244760,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f9df0985706e172b7dbf15e327022e5e0fe7a51","tid":1244760,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11a7430a323a1efa01bc448c64c1f42c859941eb","tid":1244760,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c37c45c10050ae4dfcc420982ef39ffbefaba66c","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"簽"},{"pid":"977991e258ac62c2fda1165d17e5fb65943c90a7","tid":1244760,"uid":259423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:53:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e81aebddc57f6fd57d1189f2181b3d98fc50c8c5","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"和打機一樣，當你見到路上充滿敵人，就知道走對路了。<br />\n<br />\n有人問聯署字眼為何這樣，為何不具體，為何行文如此。<br />\n聯署是政治把戲，不是講道理，不是交計劃書。單一、出眾、Wild card，甚至用當撈侵行文的方式，令訊息夠punching，模糊是令當撈侵可以出wild card，做什麼也行，總統做嘢唔洗你教。<br />\n<br />\n至於有人說「我不喜愛當撈侵，不簽。」就是不動動你的蠢腦，適當時候做適當事，現在不是叫你投他一票。<br />\n<br />\n然後有人說這就是港獨，這不是港獨，是借美國對中共威脅，協助鞏固香港的實然主權，維持香港特殊的地位，並推動雙普選，完全合法合憲。先鞏固實際的自主權，港不港獨是之後的事，你和港獨派往後慢慢討論，不關這事。<br />\n<br />\n即刻簽，立刻簽，好好睇睇，多少少人，當撈侵好說話一點。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7966050e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation</a><br />\n簽完記得去email 按確認！"},{"pid":"25378f89c1a55bf1983b3a55bae012b727c77159","tid":1244760,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64a75c2c00d5e2574545dd9c6d4045c79f9e0929","tid":1244760,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389ced25af6ab155b3089b767b6fa9ac38071c70","tid":1244760,"uid":73057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:03:22.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"d6334f64832f56c4e2d65a9e0b6e0a750273c18e","tid":1244760,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:05:30.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"ecbfe7e2b358ce2cccee50e1acc15735bd364819","tid":1244760,"uid":131282,"like":0,"disli